{
  "stem": "294.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said that people are being exterminated there in the-- I don't think they had a-- a crematoria yet, but in the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody believed him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we heard rumors, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we didn't believe it, because, you see, God forbid, it would happen now.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a precedent in history.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We would be maybe watchful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe we will be more frightened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in those days, there was no precedent in history.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Who could visualize that a man is capable to do something like this to another man?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Poldek was working.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do I remember?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Poldek was working-- where was he working at that time?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He will tell you himself, because I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because he-- in the camp, he did several things, and I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this was not the food that the Germans-- this was not the German allowance.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody tried to buy something on a black market.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were, you know, this was in the city of Krakow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The ghetto's walls were closed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But a lot of Polish people were coming and selling by the-- you know, somehow the food was getting into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe the police brought it in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe-- I don't know who.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans and the Polish police.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Polish police was mostly like the helpers of the German police.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only when I was working, I was going with a group.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Poldek-- I know now what Poldek was doing-- now-- now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was at the beginning of the ghetto when I think that-- that you could get out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yeah, the ghetto wasn't closed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he had his bicycle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he also had to sell certain things on the black market, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and this is how we lived.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
